{"tid":1310433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連儂牆=派傳單升級版 但唔會為派傳單而錯失行動","createTime":"2019-07-12T16:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T16:20:46.000Z","uid":57614,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"40b833ca15472b9145163389014ae4db86f4d53e","tid":1310433,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"大家明未? 未開始連儂牆之前 大家唔會亂吹雞「要人」  緊急同重要資訊post會推得好快<br />\n開始搞連儂牆之後 日日都突發要人出黎睇連儂牆 成個連登都係連儂牆 已經有人一早講今日去搵民建聯又唔夠人 為左幅牆搞到自己<span style=\"color: red;\">無機動性</span> be water be左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有無人記得621 be water唔同政府機構</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  依家反而就死守幅牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣工作同牆當然要做 仲好緊要 但我希望大家要有分寸<span style=\"color: red;\">死守幅牆而無得be water 你對唔對得住7.1既義士?</span>"},{"pid":"cc598d8809f33c1b88b093d331aa76cd599063d6","tid":1310433,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"死都保住幅牆 又唔見大家6.30去保住梁義士既壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0095aad073435f00cad90b2427c0a85a9ea09b1f","tid":1310433,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc598d8809f33c1b88b093d331aa76cd599063d6","tid":1310433,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"死都保住幅牆 又唔見大家6.30去保住梁義士既壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知自己做緊乜?"},{"pid":"86a731bf8e3fdf039930c6fd8791dbca94362ee6","tid":1310433,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:14:56.000Z","msg":"為左幅牆日日被藍絲be water<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   反而我地唔係be water 政府?"},{"pid":"9c82abc0a5d84ff72019779f7b09f709f41f9ad8","tid":1310433,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote